01:58:06,776 --> 01:58:09,316
l suppose every time
you see those three words,

2236
01:58:09,404 --> 01:58:11,574
your puny chest
will swell with pride

2237
01:58:11,656 --> 01:58:14,316
over your great
historical contribution.

2238
01:58:14,409 --> 01:58:15,529
lt's more memorable

2239
01:58:15,618 --> 01:58:17,738
than your
unprincipled
whitewash

2240
01:58:17,829 --> 01:58:19,829
of that race
of barbarians!

2241
01:58:19,914 --> 01:58:22,374
Race of barbarians?
(ALL SHOUTlNG)

2242
01:58:22,458 --> 01:58:23,748
Why, l'll have you. . .

2243
01:58:24,377 --> 01:58:26,747
Colonel McKean,
Mr. Read, that's enough !

2244
01:58:29,340 --> 01:58:30,970
Mr. Hopkins.
l've no objections,
Johnny.

2245
01:58:31,050 --> 01:58:32,760
l'm just trying
to get a drink.

2246
01:58:32,844 --> 01:58:35,644
l should've known.
McNair, get him a rum.

2247
01:58:40,977 --> 01:58:42,347
Mr. Bartlett.

2248
01:58:43,146 --> 01:58:44,306
Mr. Jefferson.

2249
01:58:44,731 --> 01:58:47,521
l beg you to remember
that we still have
friends in England.

