to the British Parliament
in your declaration.

2276
01:59:58,513 --> 02:00:01,143
Do you think
it's wise to alienate
that august body

2277
02:00:01,224 --> 02:00:02,394
in light of
our contention

2278
02:00:02,475 --> 02:00:05,095
that they've never
had any authority
over us anyway?

2279
02:00:05,186 --> 02:00:07,596
This is a revolution,
damn it!

2280
02:00:07,688 --> 02:00:09,768
We're going to have
to offend somebody.

2281
02:00:09,857 --> 02:00:11,437
Brother Hancock!

2282
02:00:11,526 --> 02:00:12,526
(ALL SPEAKlNG lNDlSTlNCTLY)

