You'll give yourself
an attack of apoplexy
if you're not careful.

2285
02:00:20,493 --> 02:00:21,543
Have you heard what
they're doing to it?

2286
02:00:21,619 --> 02:00:22,739
Have you heard?
l heard.

2287
02:00:22,829 --> 02:00:24,039
And, so far,
that's just
our friends.

2288
02:00:24,122 --> 02:00:26,292
Can you imagine
what our enemies
will do?

2289
02:00:26,374 --> 02:00:29,134
HANCOCK: The word
"parliament" will be
removed wherever it occurs.

2290
02:00:29,210 --> 02:00:30,540
They won't
be satisfied
till they remove

2291
02:00:30,628 --> 02:00:32,418
one of the "F's"
from Jefferson's name.

2292
02:00:32,505 --> 02:00:35,295
Courage, John.
lt won't last
much longer.

2293
02:00:38,553 --> 02:00:40,053
Mr. Dickinson.

2294
02:00:40,555 --> 02:00:42,595
DlCKlNSON: Mr. Jefferson,

2295
02:00:42,682 --> 02:00:44,562
l have very little
interest in your paper,

2296
02:00:44,642 --> 02:00:46,182
as there's
no doubt
in my mind

2297
02:00:46,269 --> 02:00:48,349
that we've all but
heard the last of it.

2298
02:00:48,437 --> 02:00:51,017
But l am curious
about one thing.

2299
02:00:51,983 --> 02:00:55,403
Why do you refer
to King George
as a tyrant?

2300
02:00:57,113 --> 02:00:58,993
Because he
is a tyrant.

2301
02:00:59,991 --> 02:01:01,451
l remind you,
Mr. Jefferson,

2302
02:01:01,534 --> 02:01:03,954
that this tyrant
is still your king.

2303
02:01:05,663 --> 02:01:07,913
When a king
becomes a tyrant,

2304
02:01:07,999 --> 02:01:09,539
he thereby
breaks the contract

2305
02:01:09,625 --> 02:01:11,585
binding his
subjects to him.

2306
02:01:11,669 --> 02:01:13,299
How so?

2307
02:01:13,379 --> 02:01:15,509
By taking away
their rights.

2308
02:01:15,590 --> 02:01:18,550
Rights that
came from him
in the first place?

2309
02:01:18,634 --> 02:01:20,344
All except one.

2310
02:01:20,428 --> 02:01:23,138
The right to be free
comes from nature.

2311
02:01:24,015 --> 02:01:26,975
And are we not free,
Mr. Jefferson?

2312
02:01:29,187 --> 02:01:31,307
Homes entered
without warrant.

2313
