Citizens arrested
without charge.

2314
02:01:34,609 --> 02:01:35,609
And in many places,

2315
02:01:35,693 --> 02:01:37,993
free assembly
itself denied.

2316
02:01:38,070 --> 02:01:40,820
No one approves
of such things,

2317
02:01:40,907 --> 02:01:43,197
but these are
dangerous times.

2318
02:01:43,284 --> 02:01:44,994
Be careful,
Mr. Dickinson.

2319
02:01:45,077 --> 02:01:46,617
Those who give up
some of their liberty

2320
02:01:46,704 --> 02:01:49,164
in order to
obtain a little
temporary safety,

2321
02:01:49,248 --> 02:01:51,748
deserve neither
liberty nor safety.

2322
