by my count,

2353
02:03:06,534 --> 02:03:08,454
85 separate changes,

2354
02:03:08,536 --> 02:03:11,956
and the removal of
close to 400 words.

2355
02:03:12,039 --> 02:03:15,169
Now, would you
whip it and beat it till
you break its spirit?

2356
02:03:15,251 --> 02:03:17,131
l tell you
that document

2357
02:03:17,211 --> 02:03:18,881
is a masterful expression

2358
02:03:18,963 --> 02:03:20,923
of the American mind !

2359
02:03:26,137 --> 02:03:27,797
lf there are
no more changes,

2360
02:03:27,888 --> 02:03:31,348
then l can assume
the report of the Declaration
Committee has been. . .

2361
02:03:31,475 --> 02:03:33,475
Just a moment,
Mr. President.

2362
02:03:34,478 --> 02:03:35,728
Look out.

2363
02:03:37,148 --> 02:03:39,688
l wonder if we might prevail
upon Mr. Thomson

2364
