another hemisphere,

2374
02:04:10,514 --> 02:04:12,104
"Determined to
keep open a market

2375
02:04:12,183 --> 02:04:14,143
"where men should
be bought and sold,

2376
02:04:14,226 --> 02:04:15,266
"he has prostituted his. . ."

2377
