to our slaves.

2385
02:04:33,871 --> 02:04:39,671
Black slaves.

2386
02:04:40,878 --> 02:04:43,128
Why didn't you
say so, sir?

2387
02:04:43,214 --> 02:04:45,804
Were you trying to
hide your meaning?

2388
02:04:46,550 --> 02:04:47,800
No, sir.

2389
02:04:47,885 --> 02:04:50,715
Just another
literary license, then.

2390
02:04:51,847 --> 02:04:53,217
lf you like.

2391
02:04:54,100 --> 02:04:56,600
l don't like at all,
Mr. Jefferson.

2392
02:04:57,645 --> 02:04:59,145
To us,
in South Carolina,

2393
02:04:59,230 --> 02:05:01,690
black slavery is
our peculiar institution,

2394
02:05:01,774 --> 02:05:03,574
and a cherished
way of life.

2395
02:05:03,651 --> 02:05:06,491
Nevertheless,
we must abolish it.

2396
02:05:06,570 --> 02:05:09,610
Nothing is more
certainly written
in the book of fate

2397
