Then l'm sorry,

2421
02:06:31,739 --> 02:06:33,359
for you've
also resolved

2422
02:06:33,449 --> 02:06:35,829
the ruination of
your personal economy.

2423
02:06:35,910 --> 02:06:38,290
JOHN: Economy.
Always economy.

2424
02:06:39,413 --> 02:06:42,423
There's more to this
than a filthy purse
string, Rutledge.

2425
02:06:42,500 --> 02:06:44,580
lt's an offense
against man and God.

2426
